                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280221-176-off933 t18280221-176-cd934"></join>, 2 bushels of coals, value 2s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18280221-176-victim1065" type="victimName">
                        William 
                        Yool
                     <interp inst="t18280221-176-victim1065" type="surname" value="Yool"></interp>
